This project is a macOS graphical manager for nginx+njs 302 direct-link
workflows built around the upstream embyExternalUrl project.

Upstream project:
- Name: bpking1/embyExternalUrl
- URL: https://github.com/bpking1/embyExternalUrl
- License: MIT License
- Upstream copyright notice: Copyright (c) 2022 jerry1119

The manager may download or synchronize scripts from the upstream repository
at runtime when the user chooses upstream sync. Users and distributors should
also review and comply with the upstream project's license and notices.

